.EE
.PP
\f[B]Behavior:\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
If no target is passed, Tildr opens an interactive picker
.IP \[bu] 2
Editor resolution order: \f[CR]$EDITOR\f[R], then \f[CR]$VISUAL\f[R],
then \f[CR]nano\f[R]
.IP \[bu] 2
Edits are made directly in the repository file; the symlink in
\f[CR]$HOME\f[R] reflects the change immediately
